<article id="post-1566" class="post-1566 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-april category-debian-fr category-planet-cullt category-python category-vrac-mini-messages tag-bootstrap tag-chaos-monkey tag-collectl tag-debian tag-django tag-mini-debconf-paris tag-pagekite tag-redis tag-vaurien tag-weboob">

	
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://carlchenet.com/2012/11/02/vrac-de-mini-messages-n1/" rel="bookmark">Vrac de mini-messages&nbsp;n°1</a></h1>
					<span class="cat-links"><a href="http://carlchenet.com/category/april/" rel="category tag">april</a>, <a href="http://carlchenet.com/category/debian-fr/" rel="category tag">debian-fr</a>, <a href="http://carlchenet.com/category/planet-cullt/" rel="category tag">planet-cullt</a>, <a href="http://carlchenet.com/category/python/" rel="category tag">python</a>, <a href="http://carlchenet.com/category/vrac-mini-messages/" rel="category tag">vrac-mini-messages</a></span>
		
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

					<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Suivez-moi <a title="Carl Chenet sur Identi.ca" href="http://identi.ca/carlchenet" target="_blank">aussi sur Identi.ca</a> ou <a title="Carl Chenet sur Twitter" href="http://twitter.com/carl_chenet" target="_blank">sur Twitter</a>.</p>
<p>En vrac <strong>les mini-messages</strong> postés par votre serviteur sur <a title="Carl Chenet sur Identi.ca" href="http://identi.ca/carlchenet" target="_blank">mon Identi.ca</a>, qui aborde des sujets aussi divers que Django, Redis, Debian, et bien d&rsquo;autres. Contenu dépouillé mais qui a l&rsquo;intérêt d&rsquo;attirer l&rsquo;attention sur différents sujets <strong>à découvrir ou redécouvrir</strong>.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Django</strong> <strong>documentation</strong> is now available <strong>in ePub format</strong> <a title="https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/1.4/" href="http://ur1.ca/aqg0d" rel="external">http://ur1.ca/aqg0d</a> =&gt; très bonne initiative pour <strong>développer l&rsquo;utilisation du ePub</strong> pour les documentations techniques.</li>
<li>I have to try <strong>weboob</strong> one of these days <a title="http://weboob.org/" href="http://weboob.org/" rel="external">http://weboob.org/</a></li>
<li><strong>redis 2.6</strong> is out <a id="attachment-73992922" title="https://raw.github.com/antirez/redis/2.6/00-RELEASENOTES" href="http://ur1.ca/angud" rel="external">http://ur1.ca/angud</a> =&gt;</li>
<li>to add in my toread list <strong>The Lean Startup</strong> <a title="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lean_Startup" href="http://ur1.ca/amnba" rel="external">http://ur1.ca/amnba</a></li>
<li>Using <strong>bootstrap for a web site</strong>, quite impressed by the result <a title="http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/" href="http://ur1.ca/50vu3" rel="external">http://ur1.ca/50vu3</a> =&gt; fait, sur le site de mon projet <a title="Site officiel du logiciel Backup Checker" href="http://www.backupchecker.org" target="_blank">Backup Checker</a>. <strong>Très satisfait</strong> du résultat.</li>
<li>New blog post (fr): <strong>Mini-Debconf Paris 2012</strong> <a title="http://carlchenet.com/2012/10/22/mini-debconf-paris-2012/" href="http://ur1.ca/am0kh" rel="external">http://ur1.ca/am0kh</a> =&gt; grand succès, <strong>un public venu nombreux</strong>, des conférences très intéressantes et un bon merchandising pour faire connaître Debian.</li>
<li>Vaurien:TCP proxy which will let <strong>you simulate chaos</strong> between your application and a backend server <a title="http://vaurien.readthedocs.org/en/latest/" href="http://ur1.ca/alxs8" rel="external">http://ur1.ca/alxs8</a></li>
<li>really interesting idea about testing the resilience of your infrastructure <strong>Chaos Monkey by Netflix guys</strong> <a title="http://techblog.netflix.com/2012/07/chaos-monkey-released-into-wild.html" href="http://ur1.ca/alw21" rel="external">http://ur1.ca/alw21</a></li>
<li>need to try <strong>pagekite, the fast, reliable localhost tunneling solution</strong> <a title="https://pagekite.net/" href="https://pagekite.net/" rel="external">https://pagekite.net/</a></li>
<li><strong>collectl</strong> seems to be a great tool. I have to give it a try <a title="http://collectl.sourceforge.net/" href="http://ur1.ca/u0vz" rel="external">http://ur1.ca/u0vz</a></li>
<li>Interesting discussion at work about <strong>application deployment and reliability of the process</strong>. I love Debian packages.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Et vous ?</strong> Que pensez-vous <strong>des technologies et articles</strong> abordés ci-dessus ? N&rsquo;hésitez pas à laisser votre témoignages dans les commentaires.</p>
